 and redistributing it\nto the rest modes. As for the zonal flow, it does not have a linear source and\nis fed by nonlinear interactions of the rest modes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 18 Aug 2018 23:45:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Nov 2018 10:42:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-21"}
