Fourier transforms. Eventually, we report results of\nnumerical experiments with a discretized version of the latter algorithm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 19 Aug 2018 09:41:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-21"}
